Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.08,0:00:04.01,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,260)\fad(400,400)}生\N\N日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.28,0:00:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为名乃开生日会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.45,0:00:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那你就得事先告诉我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么准备都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  今天也不是名乃的生日啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没问过她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.07,0:00:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士的生日会也一起办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  真是一石二鸟  办吧办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种意外惊喜  不管是策划的还是接受的都很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我知道了  那大家就在回家路上去买蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  麻衣OK吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.27,0:00:54.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这里的钱包专指那种金属卡口蛙口型小钱包。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.27,0:00:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘带钱包了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.12,0:00:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:01:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么祐子就和我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.11,0:01:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也忘记带钱包了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前去游乐园弄掉的钱还没还你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之今天就由我来出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我去对名乃说「我们给你办生日会」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊喜到哪里去了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  祐子是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你明明被笹原学长甩掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我没有被甩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明哭着逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…  话说他们只是挽着手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不知道他们是否有在交往对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有向他本人确认
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说还没有完全被甩不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我还没有完全放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是很喜欢他的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:17.56,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,290)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N110
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  没有忘带的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  那我出门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我做了个「小家伙」  所以取下来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  「小家伙」是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小家伙」就是  我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西能让背上变得光滑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然小  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早你们就在做什么啊  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼  你又造了什么陷阱啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本把小家伙弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本把名乃弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  是把它乱放的你的错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  你忘带东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能马上重做一个的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来之前能做好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我现在就去做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  我去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:27.75,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,335)\fad(500,00)\fs40}校\N长\N与\N教\N导\N主\N任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教导主任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是以前我还在校长的王座上时期的铜像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊  这里应该放着的是东云校长的才对啊  好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  最近的年轻人的恶作剧该说是幽默呢还是恶趣味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是有支持者的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主任老师  搬运完毕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座铜像这样放就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教导主任  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真是的  最近年轻人的恶作剧让人怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是花心思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉  这座铜像也运走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  要把这便宜货收拾掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便宜货…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  那我就把这土里土气的东西搬走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土里土气…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  把这碍事的东西搬走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  教导主任  不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么把刚才那座愚蠢的铜像也搬走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:58.18,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,340)\fad(500,00)}围\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N8
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  门没锁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  关口你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为我是第一个到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:19.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}也就是SR-71高空战略侦察机，爱称黑鸟。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还特地乘了黑鸟来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  关口要来早练吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  那个…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:56.95,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(50,290)\fad(600,00)}日\N常\N之\N111
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的午饭居然都要我出钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:07:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  没带钱包也是没办法的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是美绪  给你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  祐子你打太重了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来  祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有问过名乃今天有空吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  完全忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我就去和她说办生日会的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就问下今天有没有空就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了我去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…  麻衣麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moment please
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just moment please
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我稍微去名乃那儿一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要成纯咖啡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要说对不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}中奖了  如果中奖可以再来一瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相…相生同学  在走廊上要安静…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  我正在找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  实际上…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗  不痛吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  这不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  比起这个  今天可以去名乃家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是惊喜  我不会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就回见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么也去买相生同学他们的份吧
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后出布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱出哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.88,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,290)\fad(600,00)}日\N常\N之\N112
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个南瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好硬！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  那小鬼为什么要一次又一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大将吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中…中村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在找你  大将  没事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要逃走啊  忘记我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有忘记才要逃走的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了大将  不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了大将
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗白白了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:34.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}机器人研究  和猫生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  不快点出门会迟到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将  那么我就出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将  快出来啊  大将
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快走啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  中村老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:13:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东云
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘  快做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在干什么  是在找什么东西吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：扑火的是夏天的蛾子。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫扑火的夏天机器人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是东云在学校什么时候都能见到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要优先找大将
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  东云  你有看到一只黑猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中村老师家有黑猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  但是不见了的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家也有一只黑猫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮您一起找可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  东云
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了中村老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师的猫的名字叫做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有意思的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家黑猫的名字叫做阪本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将  可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在说什么啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  中村也没有什么恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:23.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}关于笨手笨脚的中村的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  老这么出岔子我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:25.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}关于恶作剧小鬼的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等等  现在不也没有改变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天平不会移动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…已经这个时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  中村老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多该回去了  食物的新鲜度…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是找到了  我能去看大将吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  什么时候都行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可恶  无论去哪边都糟透了啊
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:08.05,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,290)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N113
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  阪本先生  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了吗  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被阪本踩坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  取下来可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就做一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如此简单就能取下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己想取下来却完全没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为名乃自己取不了  要别人取才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果是名乃自己就能装上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么机能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说博士  那个小家伙有什么机能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是取下来的话  大拇趾就飞不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那个机能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是相生同学他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  得把发条收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就能看上去像个普通人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能比现在更融入大家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家出去玩的时候  都能更普通地享受了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日常生活在等着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  比起这个  今天可以去名乃家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃就是名乃  这样就好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我是为了说这句话而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是重要的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们买蛋糕来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日…  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是惊喜哦  惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:19:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕  我要吃蛋糕  蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  博士  别着急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家为什么会知道啊  我的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}名乃的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小家伙做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然确实这个发条带来了很多不便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我超级想要取下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我保持这个样子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小家伙其实是个名乃高兴的时候发条会转起来的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  你能把这个蛋糕端出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一个蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把茶端过去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕  蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你们俩在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生同学  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  快找个东西擦一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里插上蜡烛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾  博士我也要插
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:21:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  在这之前先要做好准备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦的东西  擦的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  那个那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再插一根
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  先要准备好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  快停下  快停下
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
